Code accompanying this paper: Zachary M. Boyd, Nicolas Fraiman, Jeremy L. Marzuola, Peter J. Mucha, Braxton Osting, and Jonathan Weare, A metric on directed graphs based on hitting probabilities, SIAM J. Math. Data Sci., 3(2), pp. 467â€“493. by Boyd et al.

To compute the metric, check get_dhp.m.

To replicate examples from the paper, check the files fig_*.

This code should be useful any other users, but if you run into issues, feel free to email zachboyd@byu.edu with issues, and I will try to help.

Added code by Or Feldman at Technion
